                      SELZ CAPITAL LLC
                    

•   NEW YORK, NY
                          • Investment Advisor
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Selz Capital is based out of New York. Selz Capital is a large advisory firm with  11-25 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $773,259,000 (Form ADV from 2017-03-16).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $383,949,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 66.08%. Selz Capital's largest holding is Macquarie Infrastructure Company LLC with shares held of 1,024,020.  Selz Capital has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 53 13Fs and  12 13D/G filings in our database for Selz Capital. 
                                           






