            Business Description
        



Selz Capital is located in New York, New York. This organization primarily operates in the Investors, nec business / industry within the Holding and Other Investment Offices sector. This organization has been operating for approximately 10 years. Selz Capital is estimated to generate $78.2 million in annual revenues, and employs approximately 2 people at this single location.









